{"word":"G2670 - καταποντίζω - katapontízō - kat-ap-on-tid'-zo - Drown","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταποντίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katapontízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-ap-on-tid'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Drown</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அமிழ்ந்துபோ"},{"paragraph":"to sink, to go down"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and a derivative of the same as <a href=\"#/G4195 - Πόντος - Póntos - pon'-tos/4195\">G4195</a>; to <i>plunge down</i>, that is, <i>submerge:</i> - drown, sink.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}